show.description: Isabella doesn’t remember her past, but her enemies haven’t forgotten a thing. Betrayed by blood and tangled in love, she must survive a sister’s wrath and a lover’s lies. The Dumb Billionaire Heiress In Love Part II is where innocence meets manipulation. Watch Now !
